{"tid":357433,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大咗 圈子唔同咗 好多嘢先發現以前冇珍惜","createTime":"2017-08-12T21:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T02:24:47.000Z","uid":135762,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0097ee36e869451b403349c6c5fe530b4be5dff3","tid":357433,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:21:40.000Z","msg":"依家個個都返工返學intern<br />\n好多以前啲舊同學舊fd好想約出嚟都約唔岩時間<br />\n同埋大個左身邊啲人同學同事都係<br />\n工利主義 酒肉朋友 心計 憨尻仔 乜人都有<br />\n相反以前讀書嗰班真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前有約 搞啲咩活動都hea尻 冇心搞 &mdash;&gt;搞唔成<br />\n依家念起都好後悔以前點解過得咁平凡<br />\n幾時先可以搵返班同聲同氣嘅fd出嚟齊齊整整咁玩<br />\n同班酒肉朋友戴住面具做人真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf603d570400f087a259f7125275034c0b8df36c","tid":357433,"uid":131541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"你係咩人咪吸引番d咩朋友囉"},{"pid":"032e60a08ea496dbebd525d6aad0000e2e431590","tid":357433,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T00:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咩人咪吸引番d咩朋友囉</blockquote><br />\n點解好似講得咁有道理咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855fc0f6ffb527a14ade57c9e0c3584b2aa9b6c2","tid":357433,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T00:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咩人咪吸引番d咩朋友囉</blockquote><br />\n咁無朋友即係點"},{"pid":"3f3bef43e686565a75900989c6556301bdb89e12","tid":357433,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"中學時期既朋友反而歴久常新"},{"pid":"195d169f7df275dc3629f534197443938db4430f","tid":357433,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime